{"tid":783118,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"科學家令老鼠再生視網膜 盲人有望重見光明","createTime":"2018-08-17T09:53:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T10:42:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2452606a1ca063361ebe283342c5f00faf89a1ff","tid":783118,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:53:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180817/20478346\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180817%2F20478346&d=bO0u9ZGjfLMWtTGwNArufKMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=343026cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180817%2F20478346&h=acf0f8f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180817/20478346</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月17日 <br />\n<br />\n科學家令老鼠再生視網膜<br />\n盲人有望重見光明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180817/large/eye.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180817%2Flarge%2Feye.jpg&h=90030ff8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國華裔科學家利用基因療法，成功讓先天失明的老鼠開眼，是科學界首次令哺乳類動物身上受損視網膜細胞再生的案例，為日後治療人類遺傳盲疾帶來曙光。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首宗哺乳類動物成功案例<br />\n<br />\n紐約西奈山醫學院神經及眼科學教授陳波前日在英國《自然》科學雜誌發表研究成果，他領導的團隊對失明老鼠的視網膜細胞進行基因移植及重新編碼，成功激活其「米勒神經膠質」（M&uuml;ller glia）一直封存的感光細胞再生能力，實驗老鼠在六周後恢復視覺。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n實驗的靈感源自斑馬魚（Zebrafish），牠們的視網膜內保存有「米勒神經膠質」等幹細胞群，當視網膜受損，這些幹細胞會自動補充失去的神經元。雖然哺乳類動物也有「米勒神經膠質」，卻沒有斑馬魚的強大細胞自我修復能力。陳波說：「基本結構仍在，只是某些原因令功能受阻。」<br />\n<br />\n陳波團隊通過基因編碼，激活了失明老鼠的「米勒神經膠質」細胞再生能力，讓其分裂並發育成為可以感應暗光的視桿細胞（rods），他說：「今次研究重要之處，是可望廣泛應用在視網膜退化疾病上（圖）。<br />\n<br />\n有朝一日將改變我們治療視網膜疾病的方法，甚至有機會用來根治青光眼等眼疾。」<br />\n美國國家眼科研究所神經科學權威格林韋爾形容，陳波的發現是重大突破，「若果眼睛內的視桿細胞可以重生，意味在治療感光體受損的眼疾上將可另闢蹊徑。」<br />\n<br />\n英國《泰晤士報》  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n涉走私貨品入朝　美制裁中俄公司<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n印度前總理瓦杰帕伊病逝"},{"pid":"bcc869d8254ce6739064198223e3ea3cd808dec7","tid":783118,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:54:15.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"ce735a25bd0f378e8b31180b5e3bf430c29ea952","tid":783118,"uid":133528,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:58:56.000Z","msg":"人 = 老鼠?"},{"pid":"c8830bb11fb8ccddb01263b047f6f99eff8b051b","tid":783118,"uid":77355,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ce735a25bd0f378e8b31180b5e3bf430c29ea952","tid":783118,"uid":133528,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:58:56.000Z","msg":"人 = 老鼠?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T10:00:03.000Z","msg":"科技係會進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8eae02ca81021ab43b96ff068a6102340cd35cf","tid":783118,"uid":87506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T10:01:51.000Z","msg":"等多十年都唔知有無人類份"},{"pid":"d94aca8370ae7191e07371f565672846bca12f07","tid":783118,"uid":52595,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T10:08:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"20834ba937288dff03ad91a7290b2a562195b49c","tid":783118,"uid":167464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T10:10:06.000Z","msg":"年年都有類似嘅新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f1cce1992a1ce44ad07ae2bd8caa1134cd2967e","tid":783118,"uid":147047,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T10:10:32.000Z","msg":"發明者會失蹤"},{"pid":"c1ccbb7c596c4141f4e63fe3ba6f90b768b6c829","tid":783118,"uid":156618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f1cce1992a1ce44ad07ae2bd8caa1134cd2967e","tid":783118,"uid":147047,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T10:10:32.000Z","msg":"發明者會失蹤"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T10:34:54.000Z","msg":"一係就勁撚貴"},{"pid":"830ed8cd3d31f735d62cebdda2125ba0f